## navigationBar.module.js

**Summary:** Declares the `navigationBar` AngularJS module with a dependency on `notifications`. Serves as the container for the main navigation bar component, which has separate implementations for desktop layout, logged-in state, and not-logged-in state.

**Dependencies:**
- app/app/pages/notifications/notifications.module.js — notifications module dependency

**Tags:** navigation, module, layout

**Implementation:** app/app/layouts/navigationBar/navigationBar.module.js
